## Endpoints in Cardbas

List of Avaliable Endpoints User: 
- `GET /province` 
#### Description
    get data province from API RAJAONGKIR

- `POST /payment`
#### Description
    post payment to MIDTRANS

- `POST /register` 
#### Description
    create account from feature register

- `POST /Login `
#### Description
    login account with email and password

- `GET /city/:id` 
#### Description
    get data city based on ProvinceId

- `POST /price/:idCity` 
#### Description
    POST city sender and recipient code to midtrans to get 


List of Avaliable Endpoints Products:

- `GET /player`
#### Description
    get all data cards

- `GET /player/:id` 
#### Description
    get 1 data cards based on ID

Below Endpoints needs authentication
- `GET /carduser` 
#### Description
    get user cart
    
- `GET /userdata` 
#### Description
    get user registered profile

- `GET /history` 
#### Description
    get data card that has been paid

- `PUT /updateuser` 
#### Description
    update registered user data

- `PATCH /update` 
#### Description
    change status on carduser table

- `POST /carduser/:playerId` 
#### Description
    post data to carduser table based on playerId

- `DELETE /carduser/:id` 
#### Description
    delete data from carduser table

    
### Global ErrorList of Available Endpoints:

- 500- Internal Server Error

  ```json
  {
    "statusCode": 500,
    "error": {
      "message": "Internal Server Error"
    }
  }
    ```